title: *PATREON PREVIEW* Flowing Fits
description:
If nobody got you, you know TF got you. The Core 4 are tapping in to support and uplift not just each other, but the entire Throw Gang. It’s International Legaché Day and the celebratory bants are unrivaled, exploring highly specialized and nuanced garm talk, merchman chaining day, The Last of the Unenlightened Stoolies, Larry’s pivot to professional modeling, ALD F/W 20, Throwing Fits’ internal press strategy, Jimmy’s boys weekend and much more for our fellow kings behind the paywall.
 
For more Throwing Fits, check us out on Patreon: www.patreon.com/throwingfits
